# Personal Prompt Additions
# 
# This file is gitignored. It is loaded at runtime and appended to the
# system prompt. Use it for personal preferences, additional constraints,
# or style guidance that should not be committed to the public repo.
#
# Examples of what belongs here:
#   - Preferred CV length or formatting quirks
#   - Tone preferences specific to you
#   - Additional DO NOT INCLUDE rules beyond what is in meta.md
#   - Specific companies or roles to always treat as T1
#   - Any other personal context the LLM should know
#
# This file will be read if it exists. If absent, the pipeline continues
# without it — no errors.

## Additional rules

# Add your personal additions below this line.
